People's Daily Commentator: A Good Start to the 14th Five-Year Plan—On Studying and Implementing the Spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference - Xinhua Net
Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, December 11 - People's Daily, December 12, commentator article: "A Good Start to the 14th Five-Year Plan—On Studying and Implementing the Spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference"
"A good start has been achieved in the '14th Five-Year Plan'," the Central Economic Work Conference held from December 8 to 10 highly praised the achievements made in my country's economic and social development over the past year.
General Secretary Xi Jinping delivered an important speech at the meeting, profoundly summarizing the economic work in 2021, deeply analyzing the current economic situation, and making major arrangements for the economic work in 2022. This speech pointed out the direction and provided fundamental guidance for us to do a good job in the economic work next year and to welcome the successful convening of the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China.
We solemnly celebrate the centenary of the founding of the Communist Party of China, officially announce the completion of building a moderately prosperous society in all respects and the achievement of the first centenary goal, and embark on a new journey of building a modern socialist country in all respects and marching toward the second centenary goal.
We convened the Sixth Plenary Session of the 19th CPC Central Committee to summarize the major achievements and historical experiences of the Party's century-long struggle, and adopted the third historical resolution in the Party's history, "Resolution of the CPC Central Committee on the Major Achievements and Historical Experiences of the Party's Century-Long Struggle." This is a political declaration for the Chinese Communists in the new era to keep their original aspiration and mission in mind, uphold and develop socialism with Chinese characteristics, and serve as a guide for action to learn from history, create the future, and realize the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
Over the past year, the world has undergone profound changes unseen in a century, and the global COVID-19 pandemic has had a complex and severe impact. The external environment has become more complex and challenging, and the tasks of COVID-19 prevention and control and economic and social development in China have been extremely arduous and difficult.
The CPC Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core has adhered to the principle of coordinating domestic and international affairs, maintaining the general principle of seeking progress while ensuring stability, calmly responding to the unprecedented changes of the century and the global pandemic, coordinating epidemic prevention and control with economic and social development, accelerating the building of a new development pattern, strengthening cross-cycle adjustments in macro policies, focusing on promoting sustained and healthy economic development, and striving to deepen reform, opening up, and innovation. It has worked hard to accomplish the arduous tasks of reform and development, and the Party and the country have achieved new and significant accomplishments in various undertakings.
The 14th Five-Year Plan got off to a good start, an important aspect of which is that new steps have been taken in building a new development pattern and new achievements have been made in high-quality development.
my country's economic development and pandemic control have maintained a leading position globally, with its strong resilience, great potential, and robust momentum continuing to emerge. The national strategic scientific and technological forces have grown rapidly, with a surge of major innovative achievements, continuously improving scientific and technological innovation capabilities, and achieving new breakthroughs in key core technologies. The resilience of the industrial chain has been enhanced, foreign trade has seen both increased volume and quality, with continued structural optimization, and new drivers of growth represented by new industries, new business models, and new formats have flourished. Reform and opening up have been deepened, with efforts focused on removing obstacles that hinder supply and demand matching and the flow of factors of production, creating new competitive advantages through high-level opening up. People's livelihoods have been effectively guaranteed, employment has continued to expand, and residents' income growth has been basically in sync with economic growth. Grain production has remained above 1.3 trillion jin for seven consecutive years, achieving the "18th consecutive bumper harvest." Ecological civilization construction has been continuously advanced, carbon peaking and carbon neutrality work has been coordinated, green and low-carbon transformation has progressed steadily, and new achievements have been made in ecological and environmental protection.
These achievements are the result of the strong leadership of the CPC Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core, the scientific guidance of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era, and the concerted efforts and hard work of the entire Party and the people of all ethnic groups across the country.
Practice has once again proven that the Party's establishment of Comrade Xi Jinping as the core of the Party Central Committee and the core of the whole Party, and the establishment of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era as the guiding ideology, are of decisive significance for the development of the Party and the country's cause in the new era and for advancing the historical process of the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
With General Secretary Xi Jinping as the core of the Party Central Committee and the core of the whole Party, leading the way, with the scientific guidance of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era, and with the unity and tenacious struggle of the whole Party and the people of all ethnic groups across the country, we will surely be able to overcome all kinds of difficulties and obstacles, create new era glories and forge new historical achievements on the new journey of building a modern socialist country in all respects.
The 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China will be held next year, which is a major event in the political life of the Party and the country.
By carrying forward the great spirit of the founding of the Party, adhering to the general principle of seeking progress while maintaining stability, fully, accurately, and comprehensively implementing the new development philosophy, accelerating the construction of a new development pattern, comprehensively deepening reform and opening up, adhering to innovation-driven development, promoting high-quality development, adhering to supply-side structural reform as the main line, coordinating epidemic prevention and control with economic and social development, coordinating development and security, continuing to do a good job in the "six stabilities" and "six guarantees," continuously improving people's livelihoods, focusing on stabilizing the overall macro-economy, keeping the economy operating within a reasonable range, and maintaining overall social stability, we will surely be able to maintain a stable and healthy economic environment, a peaceful and prosperous social environment, and a clean and upright political environment, and greet the successful convening of the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China with outstanding achievements.
Let us unite more closely around the Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core, strengthen our "Four Consciousnesses," firm up our "Four Confidences," and achieve the "Two Upholds," continuously improving our political judgment, political understanding, and political execution, and taking concrete actions to implement the decisions and plans of the Party Central Committee and continuously advance the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era.
