I was introduced by a friend and chose to come and take a look because I trusted them. My initial budget was 70,000 yuan for a basic renovation.
Once they arrived at the store, they began a series of scams.
When I first visited the store, I only showed them my floor plan. They hadn't actually measured the house, yet they were able to give me a quote saying that my 135-square-meter house could be done for 70,000 yuan. They also showed me a rough look at their materials, but I didn't know what brand they were.
Their second scam is that as soon as you arrive at the store, they will drag you to pay a deposit (and once this money is paid, you can never get it back unless you have enough experience to argue with them).
When I was hesitating about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that if I paid the deposit today, they would give me a certain discount.
This is a huge scam. I am a living example of someone who was cheated. In a moment of impulsiveness, I paid a deposit of more than 10,000 yuan.
His quote to me had many problems: 70,000 yuan did not include plumbing and electrical work, nor did it include any doors, cabinets, or bathroom fixtures, which are the major components of the basic renovation cost.
In addition to these, their service point fees are also higher than those of other companies.
I have lost trust in this company. They made me sign the contract without explaining anything to me at the beginning.
When I went to them to get my money back, they acted like they were very experienced and had a dedicated team to deal with me.
No matter what, they will insist that it is the customer's problem and that they bear no responsibility whatsoever.
They shirked responsibility in various ways, and there were many other details I don't want to go into, it's all too painful to recount. In short, don't choose them, because my friend hired them to renovate his house and the quality was poor, and they kept charging you all sorts of extra fees afterward.
What a rip-off! They used to be the fraudulent Longtou Decoration, now they've changed to Damei, and it seems they went bankrupt and changed to something else.
So please don't choose such a rip-off renovation company.
In the future, when making choices, everyone should do more research and look up information on Baidu, because home renovation is not a small expense.
